name: Scene Six (violet)
description: Manhattan: May 3, 1969. At 6:36 PM, a man walks into a photo booth. Trenton, NJ: September 01, 1927. At 6:45 PM, a rodeo cowboy juggles while spinning a laso. Everything that has ever happened, can happen, will happen, is happening at the same time. 3424x2480px
